    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The single most powerful clan in Konoha, the Hyuuga are a clan to be respected and feared. They possess the Byakugan, an eye bloodline limit that surpasses even the Sharingan in observational prowess.</p><p><b>Source:</b> Mechanics/Character_Options/Occupations/Hyuuga Clan.md</p><p><b>Category:</b> Core</p><p><b>Prerequisite:</b> Age 8+</p><p><b>Class Skills:</b> Select 2 from Balance, Chakra Control, Hide, Intimidate, Knowledge (behavioral science), Knowledge (ninja lore), Ninjutsu, Search, Sleight of Hand, Taijutsu.</p><p><b>Feat:</b> Select one from Advanced Bloodline (Byakugan), Combat Martial Arts, Defensive Martial Arts, Genin, Genius Ninja, Nin Weapons Proficiency, Ninjutsu Adept, Taijutsu Adept.</p><p><b>Wealth Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Reputation Bonus Increase:</b> +1</p><p><b>Affiliation:</b> You require 1 less success to learn Hyuuga Hujutsu techniques.</p>"
